<p><strong>Before Combat</strong> The arcane archer casts cat's grace and drinks her potion of haste. She typically prepares shock arrows as her enhance arrows ability.<br/><strong>During Combat</strong> The archer's favorite tactic is to cast greater invisibility, then make shots from a distance using true strike.<br/><strong>Base Statistics</strong> Without cat's grace, the arcane archer's statistics are <strong>Init</strong> +5; <strong>Ref</strong> +13; <strong>Ranged</strong> +2 longbow +19/+14 (1d8+2/&times;3); <strong>Dex</strong> 20; <strong>CMD</strong> 26.</p>
